Version 1.0.7 released with support to customize the routing key. By default {name}.{level}, but you can specify your own format as following:

**Django**

```
LOGGING = {
  'version': 1,
  'disable_existing_loggers': False,
  'handlers': {
    'rabbit': {
        'level': 'DEBUG',
        'class': 'python_logging_rabbitmq.RabbitMQHandler',
        'host': 'localhost',
        'routing_key_format': 'logs.{name}-{level}'
    }
  },
  'loggers': {
    'myapp': {
        'handlers': ['rabbit'],
        'level': 'DEBUG',
        'propagate': False
    }
  }
}
```

**Python**

```python
rabbit = RabbitMQHandler(
    host='localhost',
    port=5672,
    routing_key_format='logs.{name}-{level}'
)
```

